{
  "stem": "13693.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was only about two or three times.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The thing is most of the time, I was-- that I'm young.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the-- the-- it was very-- it's very hard to go in over there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "First of all, it's was-- it's was only the-- the synagogues.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The house of worship were mostly attended by the same people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were live-- we were living quite a-- quite a way from over there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the-- the services-- usually, you used to go down near-- near the house.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the house-- Vilna was a combination.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And normally, before I'm going to talk about this one, I would like to talk-- the only structure what in Vilna what was above the ground was the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH], this was already built later.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This was a round-- the-- the-- the round windows.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And under the influence of the-- in the 19, almost 20th century, the-- this was-- the pressure on the Jews was diminished.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they were allowed already to build some structure over the ground.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And probably they got it-- they got it, probably, permission from the authorities what I was talking about, later.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But if you see in Vilna, you have-- I mention in here, Vilna was the center, the culture of the Jewry.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You have the 18th century.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You have on one side, you have Zalman, the Great Gaon, with the introduction of the Mitnagdim, the introduction of the [? scholar, ?] with-- with the introduction of Zohar.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "From the other side, you have Shneur Zalman-- Shneur Zalman of Liady, with the Hasidim.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And it was a continuous fraction between them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And it was not-- it was to-- to a point almost that this was-- this was almost to a war.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
